'''天主教孔迪亞瓦教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Kundiavana}}；{{lang-en|Diocese of Kundiawa}}）是[[巴布亞紐幾內亞|巴布亞紐幾內亞]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教芒特哈根總教區|芒特哈根總教區]]。

教區成立於1982年6月8日，<ref>{{cite web |title=KUNDIAVANA* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19820608_kundiavana.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901090022/https://w2.vatican.va/content/john-paul-ii/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_jp-ii_apc_19820608_kundiavana.html |archivedate=2019-09-01 |language=la |date=1982-06-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>位於[[欽布省|欽布省]]。2004年有教友102,208人（佔轄區總人口36.5%）、十七個堂區、十九名司鐸。教區主教現時[[教座出缺|出缺]]<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 26.07.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/26/190726a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901081044/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/26/190726a.html |archivedate=2019-09-01 |language=en |date=2019-07-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-nl|亨利·特-馬爾森|Henk te Maarssen}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 12.01.2009 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/01/12/0020/00051.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-09-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190901091025/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2009/01/12/0020/00051.html |archivedate=2019-09-01 |date=2009-01-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

